<seg type="i"><rs type="inst">Wiener Volksbuchhandlung (<rs type="pers" ana="n2_63" ref="#fk__p_58200">Ignaz Brand</rs>)</rs>, VI., Gumpendorferstrasse 8</seg><lb/>
und <seg type="i"><rs type="inst"><rs type="pers" ana="n2_64" ref="#fk__p_48837"><abbr>L.</abbr> Rosner</rs></rs>, I., Franzensring 16.</seg><lb/>
